ttack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("ara","أطلق العديد من كرات النار في منطقة ببعد 5 كتل من السماء. يُلحق 30% من إجمالي أضرار الهجوم السحري لكل انفجار بالمنطقة الأرضية للمربع 3x3","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("kor","하늘에서 5블록 크기의 영역에 많은 불덩어리를 발사합니다. 3x3 블록의 지상 영역에 폭발할 때마다 총 마법 공격력의 30% 피해를 줍니다.","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("vie","Bắn nhiều quả cầu lửa vào khu vực có kích thước 5 khối từ Bầu trời. Gây 30% sát thương phép thuật trên tổng số mỗi vụ nổ lên diện tích mặt đất của khối 3x3","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("rus","Выстрелите множеством огненных шаров по площади на расстоянии 5 блоков от неба. Наносит 30% урона от магических атак от общего количества каждого взрыва по площади блока 3х3.","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("tur","Gökyüzünden 5 blok boyutunda Alana Çok sayıda Ateş Topu fırlatıldı. 3x3 Blok Zemin Alanına her Patlamada Toplamın %30 Büyü Saldırısı Hasarı verir","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("ita","Hai sparato molte palle di fuoco in un'area di 5 blocchi di dimensione dal cielo. Infligge il 30% dei danni da attacco magico del totale per ogni esplosione nell'area terrestre del blocco 3x3","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("ger","Schieße viele Feuerbälle in einer Entfernung von 5 Blöcken vom Himmel in den Bereich. Verursacht 30 % des gesamten magischen Angriffsschadens jeder Explosion auf der Bodenfläche eines 3x3-Blocks","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("ind","Tembak Banyak Bola Api ke Area sejauh 5 dimensi blok dari Langit. Menimbulkan 30% Kerusakan Serangan Ajaib dari Total setiap Ledakan ke Area Dasar Blok 3x3","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");	createText("msa","Tembak Banyak Bola Api ke Kawasan dengan 5 dimensi blok dari Sky. Menangani 30% Kerosakan Serangan Sihir daripada Jumlah setiap Letupan ke Kawasan Tanah 3x3 Blok","Shot Many Fire Balls into Area by 5 block dimension from Sky. Dealings 30% Magic Attack Damages of Total each Explosion to The Ground Area of 3x3 Block");
