createText("cn","向目标发射火球。每个火球对 3 格半径内的敌人造成总魔法攻击力的 110%。它会留下一个燃烧区域，每毫秒造成你总魔法攻击力的 10%。","Shoot a fireball at the target. Each fireball deals 110% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 3-block radius. It leaves a burning area that deals 10% of your total magic attack every millisecond.");	createText("tw","向目标发射火球。每个火球对 3 格半径内的敌人造成总魔法攻击力的 110%。它会留下一个燃烧区域，每毫秒造成你总魔法攻击力的 10%。","Shoot a fireball at the target. Each fireball deals 110% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 3-block radius. It leaves a burning area that deals 10% of your total magic attack every millisecond.");	createText("tha","ยิงลูกไฟไปที่เป้าหมาย ลูกไฟแต่ละลูกจะสร้างความเสียหาย 110% ของพลังโจมตีเวทย์มนตร์ทั้งหมดของคุณแก่ศัตรูที่อยู่ในรัศมี 3 บล็อก มันจะออกจากพื้นที่เผาไหม้ซึ่งสร้างความเสียหาย 10% ของพลังโจมตีเวทย์มนตร์ทั้งหมดของคุณทุกๆ มิลลิวินาที","Shoot a fireball at the target. Each fireball deals 110% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 3-block radius. It leaves a burning area that deals 10% of your total magic attack every millisecond.");	createText("esn","Dispara una bola de fuego al objetivo. Cada bola de fuego inflige el 110% de tu ataque mágico total a los enemigos dentro de un radio de 3 bloques. Deja un área en llamas que causa el 10% de tu ataque mágico total cada milisegundo.","Shoot a fireball at the target. Each fireball deals 110% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 3-block radius. It leaves a burning area that deals 10% of your total magic attack every millisecond.");	createText("ptb","Atire uma bola de fogo no alvo. Cada bola de fogo causa 110% do seu ataque mágico total aos inimigos em um raio de 3 quarteirões. Ele deixa uma área em chamas que causa 10% do seu ataque mágico total a cada milissegundo.","Shoot a fireball at the target. Each fireball deals 110% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 3-block radius. It leaves a burning area that deals 10% of your total magic attack every millisecond.");	createText("fra","Tirez une boule de feu 