createText("cn","向目标发射冰枪。每支长矛造成 35 + 90% 的总魔法攻击。当它撞击地面时，它会产生一个冰块，该冰块会爆炸并冻结 3 格半径内的敌人。","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("tw","向目标发射冰枪。每支长矛造成 35 + 90% 的总魔法攻击。当它撞击地面时，它会产生一个冰块，该冰块会爆炸并冻结 3 格半径内的敌人。","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("tha","ยิงหอกน้ำแข็งไปที่เป้าหมาย หอกแต่ละอันสร้างความเสียหาย 35 + 90% ของพลังโจมตีเวทย์มนตร์ทั้งหมดของคุณ เมื่อมันกระทบพื้น มันจะสร้างบล็อกน้ำแข็งที่จะระเบิดและแช่แข็งศัตรูภายในรัศมี 3 บล็อก","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("esn","Dispara una lanza de hielo al objetivo. Cada lanza inflige 35 + 90% de tu ataque mágico total. Cuando golpea el suelo, crea un bloque de hielo que explota y congela a los enemigos dentro de un radio de 3 bloques.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("ptb","Atire uma lança de gelo no alvo. Cada lança causa 35 + 90% do seu ataque mágico total. Ao atingir o solo, cria um bloco de gelo que explode e congela os inimigos em um raio de 3 quarteirões.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("fra","Tirez une lance à glace sur la cible. Chaque lance inflige 35 + 90 % de votre attaque magique totale. Lorsqu'il touche le sol, il crée un bloc de glace qui explose et gèle les ennemis dans un rayon de 3 blocs.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("jpn","ターゲットに向かって氷の槍を撃ちます。各ランスは合計魔法攻撃力の 35 + 90% を与えます。地面に当たると氷のブロックが生成され、爆発して半径 3 ブロック以内の敵を凍らせます。","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("ara","أطلق رمح الجليد على الهدف. يتعامل كل رمح مع 35 + 90% من إجمالي هجومك السحري. عندما تصطدم بالأرض، فإنها تخلق كتلة جليدية تنفجر وتجمد الأعداء داخل دائرة نصف قطرها 3 كتل.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("kor","목표물에 얼음창을 발사합니다. 각 창은 총 마법 공격력의 35 + 90%를 처리합니다. 땅에 닿으면 폭발하는 얼음 블록을 생성하고 반경 3블록 내의 적을 얼립니다.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("vie","Bắn một cây thương băng vào mục tiêu. Mỗi ngọn thương gây ra 35 + 90% tổng đòn tấn công phép thuật của bạn. Khi chạm đất, nó tạo ra một khối băng phát nổ và đóng băng kẻ địch trong bán kính 3 khối.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("rus","Выстрелите ледяным копьем в цель. Каждое копье наносит 35 + 90% от вашей общей магической атаки. Когда он падает на землю, он создает ледяную глыбу, которая взрывается и замораживает врагов в радиусе 3 блоков.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("tur","Hedefe bir buz mızrağı atın. Her mızrak toplam büyü saldırınızın %35 + %90'ını verir. Yere çarptığında, 3 blokluk bir yarıçap içindeki düşmanları patlatan ve donduran bir buz bloğu oluşturur.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("ita","Spara una lancia di ghiaccio al bersaglio. Ogni lancia infligge il 35 + 90% del tuo attacco magico totale. Quando colpisce il suolo, crea un blocco di ghiaccio che esplode e congela i nemici entro un raggio di 3 blocchi.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("ger","Schieße mit einer Eislanze auf das Ziel. Jede Lanze verursacht 35 + 90 % Ihres gesamten magischen Angriffs. Wenn es auf dem Boden aufschlägt, erzeugt es einen Eisblock, der explodiert und Feinde im Umkreis von 3 Blöcken einfriert.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("ind","Tembakkan tombak es ke sasaran. Setiap tombak menghasilkan 35+90% dari total serangan sihir Anda. Saat menyentuh tanah, ia menciptakan balok es yang meledak dan membekukan musuh dalam radius 3 blok.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");	createText("msa","Tembak tombak ais pada sasaran. Setiap tombak memberikan 35 + 90% daripada jumlah serangan sihir anda. Apabila ia mencecah tanah, ia mewujudkan bongkah ais yang meletup dan membekukan musuh dalam radius 3 blok.","Shoot an ice lance at the target. Each lance deals 35 + 90% of your total magic attack. When it hits the ground, it creates an ice block that explodes and freezes enemies within a 3-block radius.");
createText("cn","呼出冰冷的雾气，对你面前的敌人造成减速和伤害。","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("tw","呼出冰冷的雾气，对你面前的敌人造成减速和伤害。","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("tha","หายใจออกหมอกเย็นที่จะสโลว์และสร้างความเสียหายแก่ศัตรูที่อยู่ข้างหน้าคุณ","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("esn","Exhala una niebla fría que ralentiza y daña a los enemigos frente a ti.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("ptb","Expire uma névoa fria que retarda e causa danos aos inimigos à sua frente.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("fra","Expirez une brume froide qui ralentit et endommage les ennemis devant vous.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("jpn","冷たい霧を吐き出し、目の前の敵の動きを遅くしてダメージを与えます。","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("ara","قم بإخراج ضباب بارد يؤدي إلى إبطاء الأعداء الموجودين أمامك وإلحاق الضرر بهم.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("kor","앞에 있는 적의 속도를 늦추고 피해를 주는 차가운 안개를 내뿜습니다.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("vie","Thổi ra một màn sương lạnh làm chậm và gây sát thương cho kẻ địch trước mặt bạn.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("rus","Выдохните холодный туман, который замедляет и наносит урон врагам перед вами.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("tur","Önünüzdeki düşmanları yavaşlatan ve onlara hasar veren soğuk bir sis üfleyin.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("ita","Espira una nebbia fredda che rallenta e danneggia i nemici di fronte a te.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("ger","Atmen Sie einen kalten Nebel aus, der Feinde vor Ihnen verlangsamt und ihnen Schaden zufügt.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("ind","Hembuskan kabut dingin yang memperlambat dan memberikan damage pada musuh di depanmu.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");	createText("msa","Menghirup kabus sejuk yang melambatkan dan merosakkan musuh di hadapan anda.","Breathe out a cold mist that slows and damages enemies in front of you.");
createText("cn","将自己变成冰河，恢复完全健康。在此形态下，你无法施放冰枪或冰息。","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("tw","将自己变成冰河，恢复完全健康。在此形态下，你无法施放冰枪或冰息。","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("tha","แปลงร่างตัวเองเป็นธารน้ำแข็งแห่งน้ำแข็ง ฟื้นฟูสุขภาพให้สมบูรณ์ ขณะที่อยู่ในรูปแบบนี้ คุณไม่สามารถร่าย Ice Lance หรือ Ice Breath ได้","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("esn","Transfórmate en un glaciar de hielo, recuperando tu salud por completo. Mientras estás en esta forma, no puedes lanzar Ice Lance o Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("ptb","Transforme-se em uma geleira de gelo, recuperando a saúde plena. Enquanto estiver nesta forma, você não pode lançar Ice Lance ou Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("fra","Transformez-vous en glacier de glace et retrouvez votre pleine santé. Sous cette forme, vous ne pouvez pas lancer Ice Lance ou Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("jpn","自分自身を氷の氷河に変え、完全な健康状態に回復します。この形態ではアイスランスやアイスブレスを唱えることができない。","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("ara","حول نفسك إلى نهر جليدي من الجليد، لتستعيد عافيتك الكاملة. أثناء وجودك في هذا النموذج، لا يمكنك إلقاء رمح الجليد أو نفس الجليد.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("kor","얼음 빙하로 변신하여 체력을 완전히 회복합니다. 이 상태에서는 아이스 랜스나 아이스 브레스를 시전할 수 없습니다.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("vie","Biến mình thành sông băng, hồi phục sức khỏe hoàn toàn. Khi ở dạng này, bạn không thể sử dụng Ice Lance hoặc Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("rus","Превратитесь в ледяной ледник, полностью восстановив здоровье. В этой форме вы не можете использовать Ледяное Копье или Ледяное Дыхание.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("tur","Kendinizi bir buz buzuluna dönüştürün ve tam sağlığınıza kavuşun. Bu formdayken Buz Mızrağı veya Buz Nefesi kullanamazsınız.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("ita","Trasformati in un ghiacciaio di ghiaccio, recuperando la piena salute. Mentre sei in questa forma, non puoi lanciare Ice Lance o Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("ger","Verwandeln Sie sich in einen Gletscher aus Eis und erholen Sie sich wieder vollständig. In dieser Form können Sie weder „Eislanze“ noch „Eisatem“ wirken.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("ind","Ubah diri Anda menjadi gletser es, pulihkan kesehatan Anda sepenuhnya. Saat dalam bentuk ini, Anda tidak dapat menggunakan Ice Lance atau Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");	createText("msa","Ubah diri anda menjadi glasier ais, pulih kepada kesihatan penuh. Semasa dalam borang ini, anda tidak boleh menghantar Ice Lance atau Ice Breath.","Transform yourself into a glacier of ice, recovering to full health. While in this form, you cannot cast Ice Lance or Ice Breath.");
createText("cn","对目标发动双雷，对5格半径内的敌人造成总魔法攻击力500%的伤害。","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("tw","对目标发动双雷，对5格半径内的敌人造成总魔法攻击力500%的伤害。","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("tha","โจมตีฟ้าร้องสองครั้งที่เป้าหมาย สร้างความเสียหาย 500% ของพลังโจมตีเวทย์มนตร์ทั้งหมดของคุณให้กับศัตรูที่อยู่ในรัศมี 5 บล็อก","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("esn","Lanza un doble trueno al objetivo, lo que inflige el 500% de tu ataque mágico total a los enemigos dentro de un radio de 5 bloques.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("ptb","Golpeie o alvo com trovão duplo, distribuindo 500% do seu ataque mágico total aos inimigos em um raio de 5 quarteirões.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("fra","Frappez un double tonnerre sur la cible, infligeant 500 % de votre attaque magique totale aux ennemis dans un rayon de 5 blocs.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("jpn","ターゲットに二回の雷を落とし、半径 5 ブロック以内の敵に合計魔法攻撃力の 500% を与えます。","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("ara","قم بضرب الرعد المزدوج على الهدف، مما يؤدي إلى توجيه 500% من إجمالي هجومك السحري إلى الأعداء ضمن دائرة نصف قطرها 5 كتل.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("kor","대상에게 이중 천둥을 가해 5블록 반경 내의 적에게 총 마법 공격력의 500%를 적용합니다.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("vie","Tấn công sấm sét gấp đôi vào mục tiêu, gây 500% tổng đòn tấn công phép thuật của bạn lên kẻ địch trong bán kính 5 khối.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("rus","Ударьте по цели двойной гром, нанося 500% от вашей общей магической атаки врагам в радиусе 5 блоков.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("tur","Hedefe çift gök gürültüsü vurarak 5 blokluk yarıçap içindeki düşmanlara toplam büyü saldırınızın %500'ünü verir.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("ita","Colpisce un doppio tuono sul bersaglio, infliggendo il 500% del tuo attacco magico totale ai nemici entro un raggio di 5 blocchi.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("ger","Schlage doppelten Donner auf das Ziel und verursache 500 % deines gesamten magischen Angriffs bei Gegnern im Umkreis von 5 Blöcken.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("ind","Pukul guntur ganda pada target, berikan 500% dari total serangan sihir Anda ke musuh dalam radius 5 blok.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");	createText("msa","Pukul guruh berganda pada sasaran, memberikan 500% daripada jumlah serangan sihir anda kepada musuh dalam radius 5 blok.","Strike double thunder at the target, dealing 500% of your total magic attack to enemies within a 5-block radius.");
createText("cn","冲向目标位置。冲刺时可以根据目标位置改变方向，实现曲线冲刺。立即用造成你总魔法攻击 50% 的雷霆一击击中附近的敌人。","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("tw","冲向目标位置。冲刺时可以根据目标位置改变方向，实现曲线冲刺。立即用造成你总魔法攻击 50% 的雷霆一击击中附近的敌人。","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("tha","พุ่งไปยังตำแหน่งเป้าหมาย สามารถเปลี่ยนทิศทางตามตำแหน่งเล็งขณะพุ่ง ทำให้สามารถพุ่งโค้งได้ โจมตีศัตรูที่อยู่ใกล้เคียงทันทีด้วยการโจมตีสายฟ้าที่สร้างความเสียหาย 50% ของพลังโจมตีเวทย์มนตร์ทั้งหมดของคุณ","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("esn","Corre hacia la posición deseada. Puede cambiar de dirección según la posición del objetivo mientras corre, lo que permite movimientos curvos. Golpea instantáneamente a los enemigos cercanos con un trueno que inflige el 50% de tu ataque mágico total.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("ptb","Corra para a posição desejada. Pode mudar de direção de acordo com a posição da mira enquanto corre, permitindo traços curvos. Acerte instantaneamente os inimigos próximos com um trovão que causa 50% do seu ataque mágico total.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("fra","Dash vers la position visée. Peut changer de direction en fonction de la position de visée pendant le sprint, permettant des tirets incurvés. Frappez instantanément les ennemis proches avec un coup de tonnerre qui inflige 50 % de votre attaque magique totale.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("jpn","狙った位置へダッシュ。ダッシュ中に照準位置に応じて方向を変えることができ、曲線ダッシュも可能。近くの敵を雷撃で即座に攻撃し、合計魔法攻撃力の 50% を与えます。","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("ara","اندفع إلى الموضع المستهدف. يمكن تغيير الاتجاه وفقًا لموضع الهدف أثناء الاندفاع، مما يسمح بشرطات منحنية. اضرب الأعداء القريبين على الفور بضربة رعدية تسبب 50% من إجمالي هجومك السحري.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("kor","목표 위치로 돌진합니다. 대시 중 조준 위치에 따라 방향을 바꿀 수 있어 곡선 대시가 가능하다. 총 마법 공격력의 50%에 해당하는 천둥 공격을 가해 근처의 적을 즉시 공격합니다.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("vie","Lao tới vị trí mục tiêu. Có thể thay đổi hướng theo vị trí ngắm trong khi lao, cho phép lao theo đường cong. Ngay lập tức tấn công kẻ thù ở gần bằng đòn tấn công sấm sét, gây 50% tổng đòn tấn công phép thuật của bạn.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("rus","Сделайте рывок к намеченной позиции. Может менять направление в зависимости от положения цели во время рывка, позволяя совершать изогнутые рывки. Мгновенно поразите ближайших врагов ударом грома, который нанесет 50% от вашей общей магической атаки.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("tur","Hedeflenen konuma doğru ilerleyin. Atılma sırasında hedef konumuna göre yön değiştirebilir, böylece kavisli atılmalara izin verilir. Toplam büyü saldırınızın %50'sini veren bir gök gürültüsü darbesiyle yakındaki düşmanlara anında vurun.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("ita","Scatta nella posizione mirata. Può cambiare direzione in base alla posizione di mira durante lo scatto, consentendo scatti curvi. Colpisci istantaneamente i nemici vicini con un tuono che infligge il 50% del tuo attacco magico totale.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("ger","Springe zur Zielposition. Kann beim Sprinten je nach Zielposition die Richtung ändern, was gekrümmte Sprints ermöglicht. Trifft Gegner in der Nähe sofort mit einem Donnerschlag, der 50 % eures gesamten magischen Angriffs verursacht.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("ind","Lari ke posisi yang dituju. Dapat mengubah arah sesuai posisi membidik saat berlari, memungkinkan garis putus-putus melengkung. Pukul musuh terdekat secara instan dengan sambaran petir yang menghasilkan 50% dari total serangan sihir Anda.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");	createText("msa","Melompat ke kedudukan yang dituju. Boleh menukar arah mengikut kedudukan sasaran semasa berlari, membenarkan garisan melengkung. Pukul musuh berdekatan dengan serta-merta dengan serangan petir yang memberikan 50% daripada jumlah serangan sihir anda.","Dash to the aimed position. Can change direction according to aim position while dashing, allowing curved dashes. Instantly hit nearby enemies with a thunder strike that deals 50% of your total magic attack.");
createText("cn","获得每秒交替雷暴和雷霆冲刺即时冷却时间的增益效果。","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("tw","获得每秒交替雷暴和雷霆冲刺即时冷却时间的增益效果。","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("tha","ได้รับบัฟที่จะสลับคูลดาวน์ทันทีของ Thunderstorm และ ThunderDash ในแต่ละวินาที","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("esn","Obtén una mejora que alterna tiempos de reutilización instantáneos para Thunderstorm y ThunderDash cada segundo.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("ptb","Ganhe um buff que alterna recargas instantâneas para Thunderstorm e ThunderDash a cada segundo.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("fra","Bénéficiez d'un buff qui alterne les temps de recharge instantanés pour Thunderstorm et ThunderDash chaque seconde.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("jpn","サンダーストームとサンダーダッシュの即時クールダウンを毎秒交互に繰り返すバフを獲得します。","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("ara","احصل على تعزيز يتناوب فترات التهدئة الفورية لـ Thunderstorm وThunderDash في كل ثانية.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("kor","Thunderstorm과 ThunderDash의 즉시 재사용 대기시간이 매초 번갈아 바뀌는 버프를 얻습니다.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("vie","Nhận được bùa lợi xen kẽ thời gian hồi chiêu tức thì của Thunderstorm và ThunderDash mỗi giây.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("rus","Получите положительный эффект, который каждую секунду меняет мгновенное время восстановления «Громовой бури» и «Громового рывка».","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("tur","Thunderstorm ve ThunderDash için her saniye anlık bekleme sürelerini değiştiren bir güçlendirme kazanın.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("ita","Ottieni un potenziamento che alterna i tempi di recupero istantanei di Temporale e Tuonoscatto ogni secondo.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("ger","Erhalten Sie einen Buff, der die sofortigen Abklingzeiten für „Gewitter“ und „Donnerschlag“ jede Sekunde abwechselt.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("ind","Dapatkan buff yang mengganti cooldown instan untuk Thunderstorm dan ThunderDash setiap detik.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");	createText("msa","Dapatkan buff yang menggantikan cooldown segera untuk Ribut Petir dan ThunderDash setiap saat.","Gain a buff that alternates instant cooldowns for Thunderstorm and ThunderDash each second.");
createText("cn","获得每秒立即重置技能1和技能2的增益，并在一段时间后使当前生命值翻倍。","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("tw","获得每秒立即重置技能1和技能2的增益，并在一段时间后使当前生命值翻倍。","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("tha","ได้รับบัฟที่จะรีเซ็ตทักษะ 1 และทักษะ 2 ทันทีในแต่ละวินาที และเพิ่ม HP ปัจจุบันของคุณเป็นสองเท่าหลังจากช่วงระยะเวลาหนึ่ง","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("esn","Obtén una mejora que restablece la Habilidad 1 y la Habilidad 2 instantáneamente cada segundo y duplica tu HP actual después de un período de tiempo.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("ptb","Ganhe um buff que redefine a Habilidade 1 e a Habilidade 2 instantaneamente a cada segundo e dobra seu HP atual após um período de tempo.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("fra","Gagnez un buff qui réinitialise instantanément les compétences 1 et 2 chaque seconde et double vos HP actuels après un certain temps.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("jpn","スキル 1 とスキル 2 を毎秒瞬時にリセットし、一定時間後に現在の HP を 2 倍にするバフを獲得します。","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("ara","احصل على تعزيز يعمل على إعادة ضبط المهارة 1 والمهارة 2 على الفور كل ثانية ومضاعفة نقاط الصحة الحالية لديك بعد فترة من الوقت.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("kor","1초마다 스킬 1과 스킬 2가 즉시 초기화되고, 일정 시간이 지나면 현재 HP가 두 배가 되는 버프를 얻습니다.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("vie","Nhận được bùa lợi giúp thiết lập lại Kỹ năng 1 và Kỹ năng 2 ngay lập tức mỗi giây và nhân đôi lượng HP hiện tại của bạn sau một khoảng thời gian.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("rus","Получите положительный эффект, который мгновенно сбрасывает Навык 1 и Навык 2 каждую секунду и удваивает ваше текущее здоровье через определенный период времени.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("tur","Beceri 1 ve Beceri 2'yi her saniye anında sıfırlayan ve bir süre sonra mevcut HP'nizi ikiye katlayan bir güçlendirme kazanın.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("ita","Ottieni un potenziamento che ripristina istantaneamente l'Abilità 1 e l'Abilità 2 ogni secondo e raddoppia i tuoi HP attuali dopo un periodo di tempo.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("ger","Erhalten Sie einen Buff, der Fertigkeit 1 und Fertigkeit 2 jede Sekunde sofort zurücksetzt und Ihre aktuellen HP nach einer gewissen Zeit verdoppelt.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("ind","Dapatkan buff yang mereset Skill 1 dan Skill 2 secara instan setiap detik dan menggandakan HP Anda saat ini setelah jangka waktu tertentu.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");	createText("msa","Dapatkan buff yang menetapkan semula Kemahiran 1 dan Kemahiran 2 serta-merta setiap saat dan menggandakan HP semasa anda selepas satu tempoh masa.","Gain a buff that resets Skill 1 and Skill 2 instantly each second and doubles your current HP after a period of time.");
createText("cn","冲向指定位置，落地时造成总物理攻击力的200%+生命值的60%。或者，在空中时，落地时造成总物理攻击力的350%+生命值的60%。","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("tw","冲向指定位置，落地时造成总物理攻击力的200%+生命值的60%。或者，在空中时，落地时造成总物理攻击力的350%+生命值的60%。","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("tha","พุ่งไปยังตำแหน่งที่กำหนดและทำการโจมตีทางกายภาพทั้งหมด 200% + HP ทั้งหมด 60% เมื่อลงจอด อีกทางหนึ่ง เมื่ออยู่กลางอากาศ สร้างการโจมตีกายภาพทั้งหมด 350% + HP ทั้งหมด 60% เมื่อลงจอด","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("esn","Corre hacia la posición designada y aplica 200% de ataque físico total + 60% de HP total al aterrizar. Alternativamente, cuando estés en el aire, inflige 350% de ataque físico total + 60% de HP total al aterrizar.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("ptb","Corra para a posição designada e cause 200% do ataque físico total + 60% do HP total ao pousar. Alternativamente, quando estiver no ar, cause 350% do ataque físico total + 60% do HP total ao pousar.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("fra","Foncez vers la position désignée et infligez 200 % d'attaque physique totale + 60 % de PV total à l'atterrissage. Alternativement, lorsque vous êtes dans les airs, infligez 350 % d'attaque physique totale + 60 % de PV total à l'atterrissage.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("jpn","指定位置にダッシュし、着地時に合計物理攻撃力200%+合計HP60%を与える。あるいは、空中にいる場合、着地時に合計物理攻撃力 350% + 合計 HP 60% を与えます。","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("ara","اندفع إلى الموضع المحدد ونفذ هجومًا بدنيًا إجماليًا بنسبة 200% + إجمالي 60% من الصحة عند الهبوط. وبدلاً من ذلك، عندما تكون في الهواء، قم بتوجيه 350% من إجمالي الهجوم الجسدي + 60% من إجمالي الصحة عند الهبوط.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("kor","지정된 위치로 돌진해 착지 시 총 물리 공격력 200% + 총 체력 60%를 줍니다. 또는 공중에 있을 때 총 물리 공격력의 350% + 착지 시 총 체력의 60%를 줍니다.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("vie","Lao tới vị trí được chỉ định và gây 200% tổng tấn công vật lý + 60% tổng HP khi tiếp đất. Ngoài ra, khi ở trên không, gây tổng tấn công vật lý 350% + tổng HP 60% khi tiếp đất.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing. Alternatively, when in the air, deal 350% total physical attack + 60% total HP when landing.");	createText("rus","Мчитесь к указанной позиции и нанесите 200% общей физической атаки + 60% общего количества здоровья при приземлении. В качестве альтернативы, находясь в воздухе, нанесите 350% общей физической атаки + 60% общего количества здоровья при приземлении.","Dash to the designated position and deal 200% total physical attack +